                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230910-92-off520 t18230910-92-cd521"></join>, fifty-one yards and a quarter of linen cloth, value 2 l. 13 s.; one hundred and seventeen yards of other linen, value 4 l. 2 s. 3 d.; twenty-eight yards of twilled stuff, value 28 s. 6 d.; one hundred and twenty-one yards and a half of gingham, value 23 s. 3 d.; seven pieces of calico, containing twenty-eight yards each, value 5 l. 10 s. 3 d.; eight pieces of cambric muslin, containing twelve yards each, value 5 l. 4 s. 6 d.; seven yards of packing cloth, value 3 s., and a piece of hempen cord, value 1 s. 3 d.
